  "拒绝者：一会我们面对来路僵尸方向，右下方门是路，先别贴门好吧": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "Rejecter: In a moment, face the zombies coming from the entrance. The door at the bottom right is the way out. Don't hug the wall yet, okay?",
