    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "Rejecter: After the elevator goes up, there are two zombies patrolling. Shoot early to hold them off.",
      "JP": "拒否者：エレベーター上昇後、ゾンビが道を確保するまで2人提前に射撃して制圧しなさい",
